<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Male genitalia in A. gambronensis sp. n. (A, D) and A. kurdistanella Amsel (B, C, E), and phallus in S. robustus (F). A, B) main armature and phallus, C) distal part of uncus and gnathos in lateral view, D, E) distal part of phallus in lateral view, showing cornutus." , "Figure 4. Wings venation (A, B) in A. kurdistanella (A) and S. brunnealis (B), and stylized drawings of ventral ciliae of the antennae (C-E) in A. gambronensis sp. n. (C) and S. brunnealis (D, E). C, D) in ventral view, E) in lateral view, showing ciliae of the left part." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/187604" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/187606" .

